PRIVACY POLICY  FOR REST REMINDER +

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Rest Reminder + (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Colormindapps. The Application is a simple productivity tool for maintaining healthy and productive work process by having frequent breaks.

User Provided Information 
The Application does not obtain or collect any personal information. 
All preferences selected by a user are stored only in the device the Application is installed on. 
By uninstalling the Application from the device will delete any previously selected preferences.

Children
We do not use the Application to knowingly solicit data from or market to children under the age of 13.

Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here and informing you via email or text message. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes. You can check the history of this policy by clicking here.

Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at colormindapps@gmail.com.
